[It is likely, but unstated, that the food handler index case was un-immunized, and this substantial cluster could have been avoided if routine immunization of food handlers was the rule. Spillover of HAV from the multi state large epidemic involving the homeless and/or substance abusing populations into food handlers seems to be frequent, given the number of reports on Google. - Mod.LL

